---
import Landing from "../layouts/Landing.astro";
---

<Landing title="Privacy Policy — Drobu" description="Privacy Policy for Drobu clipboard manager for macOS.">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <a href="/clipboard-history/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-secondary transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to home</a>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Local-first by design</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu stores all clipboard data locally on your Mac. Your clipboard history never leaves your device. There is no cloud sync, no remote storage, and no telemetry. We cannot access your clipboard data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu the application collects no data. However, when you subscribe through our website, our payment processor (Stripe) collects:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Payment information (credit card details)</li>
        <li>Billing address (if required by your payment method)</li>
        <li>IP address and browser information (for fraud prevention)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This data is processed by Stripe in accordance with their <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy policy</a>. We do not store your payment details on our servers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">No tracking</h2>
      <p>
        The Drobu website does not use analytics, cookies, or third-party tracking scripts. We do not track your browsing behavior.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">No account system</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu does not require an account. There is no user database, no login system, and no profile data stored on our servers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Password manager compatibility</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu automatically ignores concealed items from password managers like 1Password. Transient clipboard entries and auto-generated passwords are never stored in your clipboard history.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        Clipboard history retention is configurable within the app. You control how long items are kept and can delete individual items or clear your entire history at any time. All data is stored in a local SQLite database on your Mac.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:support@drobu.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">support@drobu.app</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Landing>
